{
  "id": "adv_event_2202_01_03",
  "title": "甘くない現実",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 0.8600000024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ダメね、この企画は通せないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This plan won't work‚ it can't be approved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666666667,
      "endTime": 4.9386622111000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、僕もそう思う。こころには悪いけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think so too. Sorry‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1453288396,
      "endTime": 9.295691617300001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.495691665,
      "endTime": 10.3424717148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしてですか！？\nちゃんとリズノワらしいバレンタインを表現出来て――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Why?!\nWe were able to express a Valentine's that's truly LizNoir-like…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.5558050315,
      "endTime": 15.7838097731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、ダンスの振り付けは力強くて\n一見、僕達のイメージに合ってるように見える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ the dance choreography is powerful.\nAt first glance‚ it seems to fit our image.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9771431446,
      "endTime": 22.847551488900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、表面だけなんだよ\nテーマがないから、心に響いてこないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's only on the surface.\nIt doesn't resonate with our hearts because it lacks a theme.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0608846505,
      "endTime": 28.902086242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "核になるのは、LizNoirのバレンタイン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The core should be LizNoir's Valentine's.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "endTime": 33.0600001176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そのイメージを作曲家さんや作詞家さんに\nはっきり伝えるのがこころの仕事でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's Kokoro's job to clearly convey\nthat image to the composer and lyricist‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2666666667,
      "endTime": 38.576757812500006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに資料が多いのは、裏を返せば\nイメージに自信がなかったから。違う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having so much material means‚ on the flip side‚\nthat there wasn't confidence in the image. Isn't that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8,
      "endTime": 44.89541982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "endTime": 47.9500452518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さんと葵さんの言う通りだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Rio-san and Aoi-san are right…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "endTime": 51.1639909427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "（昨日、完成したってはしゃいでないで）\n（気が付いていれば……ごめん、こころ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Instead of getting excited about its completion yesterday…)\n(If only I had realized sooner… Sorry‚ Kokoro.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3666666667,
      "endTime": 58.8587984402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ。落ち込むな、とは言えないけど……\n君がとても頑張っていたのは、僕も莉央も知ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Kokoro. I can't tell you not to feel down‚ but…\nBoth Rio and I know how hard you've been working.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2666666667,
      "endTime": 67.3371429124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、今回は残念だったけど、こころの努力は認めるわ\nLizNoirのために頑張ったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ even though it didn't work out this time‚ I acknowledge your effort‚ Kokoro.\nYou've been working hard for LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5333333333,
      "endTime": 75.45315195719999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころ、元気出そ？\n今回は残念だったけど、いつか――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ko-Kokoro‚ cheer up‚ okay?\nIt didn't work out this time‚ but someday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6333333333,
      "endTime": 82.51047623950001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "これをバネにしてまた頑張れば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Use this as a springboard and try again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "endTime": 86.4160091877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "超絶アイドルスマイル！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Super Idol Smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6,
      "endTime": 90.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "わっ！？　こ、こころ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! K-Kokoro!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0666666667,
      "endTime": 93.196009032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "何を勘違いしてるんですか～？\nこころは、ちっっっとも落ち込んでなんかいません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you misunderstanding~?\nI'm not feeling down at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3666666667,
      "endTime": 99.8102970993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　で……でも、今震えてたよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But… you were trembling just now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0333333333,
      "endTime": 104.73866208390001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……自分の才能が凄過ぎて\n無茶震いしてただけです！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's… because my talent is too amazing‚\nso my adnareline is pumping!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9333333333,
      "endTime": 111.0665532588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、武者震いって言いたいのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you trying to say \"adrenaline\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2666666667,
      "endTime": 114.7773242633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、使い方間違ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if that's the case‚ that don't pump out now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115,
      "endTime": 117.8087075233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "場を和ませるボケですよぉ～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a funny joke to lighten the mood~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118,
      "endTime": 121.3233106613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "先輩のお二人はナイスリアクションです\nそれに比べて愛ちゃんときたら！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you senpai have nice reactions.\nBut compared to that‚ Ai-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "endTime": 126.9211118063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "次こそは、全リズノワが感動で泣く曲のイメージを\n作って見せます！　もちろん私がセンターです～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time‚ I'll create an image of a song that will make\nall of LizNoir cry with emotion! And of course‚ I'll be the center~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1333333333,
      "endTime": 134.55170059199997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　さすがにもう時間がないわ\nこころ、今回は諦めて、ちゃんと休みなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? There's really no more time.\nKokoro‚ give up on this one and take a proper rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7333333333,
      "endTime": 141.7152834892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません、莉央さん。お願いです、もう一回！\nお願いですから、もう一回だけチャンスを下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry‚ Rio-san. Please‚ one more chance!\nI'm begging you‚ please give me one more chance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9,
      "endTime": 151.1473693848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2202_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで言うなら……でも……\nこころ、貴方、どうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're saying it like that… but…\nKokoro‚ why…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3333333333,
      "endTime": 157.6140360197,
